text: Francisco Pascual Eyegue Obama Asue is an Equatoguinean politician. He has been the Prime Minister of Equatorial Guinea, from 23 June 2016 to 1 February 2023. == References == Category:Prime Ministers of Equatorial Guinea Category:Current national leaders Category:Living people Category:1949 births Category:Health ministers Category:Politics of Equatorial Guinea
